onents</t>","h":"1. Fill in the &apos;Parts&apos; sheet with all your configurable components"},{"t":"2. Fill in the 'Rules' sheet with compatibility rules (optional)","r":"<t>2. Fill in the 'Rules' sheet with compatibility rules (optional)</t>","h":"2. Fill in the &apos;Rules&apos; sheet with compatibility rules (optional)"},{"t":"3. Fill in the 'Presets' sheet with pre-built configurations (optional)","r":"<t>3. Fill in the 'Presets' sheet with pre-built configurations (optional)</t>","h":"3. Fill in the &apos;Presets&apos; sheet with pre-built configurations (optional)"},{"t":"4. Fill in the 'Categories' sheet to define how options are grouped","r":"<t>4. Fill in the 'Categories' sheet to define how options are grouped</t>","h":"4. Fill in the &apos;Categories&apos; sheet to define how options are grouped"},{"t":"GLB FILE REQUIREMENTS:","r":"<t>GLB FILE REQUIREMENTS:</t>","h":"GLB FILE REQUIREMENTS:"},{"t":"• Create ONE .glb file per category (e.g., seats.glb, wheels.glb)","r":"<t>• Create ONE .glb file per category (e.g., seats.glb, wheels.glb)</t>","h":"• Create ONE .glb file per category (e.g., seats.glb, wheels.glb)"},{"t":"• Each GLB contains ALL variants for that category","r":"<t>• Each GLB contains ALL variants for that category</t>","h":"• Each GLB contains ALL variants for that category"},{"t":"• Node names inside GLB must match the 'Node_Name' column exactly","r":"<t>• Node names inside GLB must match the 'Node_Name' column exactly</t>","h":"• Node names inside GLB must match the &apos;Node_Name&apos; column exactly"},{"t":"• Keep base/frame in a separate 'base.glb' file (always loaded first)","r":"<t>• Keep base/frame in a separate 'base.glb' file (always loaded first)</t>","h":"• Keep base/frame in a separate &apos;base.glb&apos; file (always loaded first)"},{"t":"PERFORMANCE TIPS:","r":"<t>PERFORMANCE TIPS:</t>","h":"PERFORMANCE TIPS:"},{"t":"• Keep individual GLB files under 10MB for best mobile performance","r":"<t>• Keep individual GLB files unde